Package: nwps
Title: Access the National Water Prediction Service API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Will", "Curran-Groome", email = "wcurrangroome@urban.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to access all endpoints of the National Water
    Prediction Service (NWPS) API. Retrieve gauge metadata, stage-to-flow
    ratings, observed and forecast stage/flow data, National Water Model reach
    data, and streamflow forecasts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://ui-research.github.io/nwps/, https://github.com/UI-Research/nwps, https://api.water.noaa.gov/nwps/v1/
BugReports: https://github.com/UI-Research/nwps/issues
